{"tid":1281127,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前皇家香港警察高級警司及35年《警訊》監製：四十年警隊形象一朝喪","createTime":"2019-07-03T07:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T08:12:52.000Z","uid":236878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c1527e920b8a60f6c3d6191bbea3e01432b39ba3","tid":1281127,"uid":236878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:55:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190629&amp;s=10829392&amp;a=59766321\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190629%26s%3D10829392%26a%3D59766321&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaV7KDDpXBBweeKWShnQU3kRY%3D&h=40d62fc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190629%26s%3D10829392%26a%3D59766321&h=7778d5a4\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190629&amp;s=10829392&amp;a=59766321</a><br />\n<br />\n連之前做警察的都睇唔過眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa04e9ad3fae9d07651eafb375d35022f18cf16","tid":1281127,"uid":68689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T08:12:52.000Z","msg":"她覺得，<span style=\"color: red;\">董建華政府是分水嶺。不同政府特首有不同性格，董建華相對和善，不必邀功；但到梁振英與林鄭月娥，一國兩制變了。</span>公務員的理念是為人服務，但近十年變成為老闆服務：「你是被管治的，你不聽我的你就是刁民，這個講法完全不對的。像今次對待和平地表達意願的示威者，我看片段，示威者都半昏迷了，還在地上拖行，這些一兩個鏡頭已經將辛苦建立來的、令人真心相信你是好警察的形象都破壞了。若市民不信任你，無論你的任務有多偉大 ，你都忘記了你的初心。」<br />\n<br />\n曾蔭權呢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}